text: Gloria Hallelujah Woods (born July 28, 1999), better known as GloRilla, is an American rapper. She was born in Memphis, Tennessee. In 2022, her song "F.N.F. (Let's Go)" (with producer Hitkidd) was nominated for Best Rap Performance at 65th Annual Grammy Awards. ==References== == Other websites == * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Rappers from Tennessee Category:African-American rappers Category:21st-century American singer- songwriters Category:Singers from Memphis, Tennessee Category:American trap musicians Category:American crunk singers Category:American hip hop musicians
